{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_00_01","textHome":"我是，五十铃怜……嗯。我……特别@不擅长……说话。那个……不管想说什么……@总是说不好……大概也经常让对方很着急……@嗯。要是那样……真的很抱歉。提、提前说声@对不起…可能比较好……嗯……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":14.5,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":9.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":1}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_00_18","textHome":"将来的梦想我已经想好了。@我想在文章里稍微放进一些插画……嗯，@这是叫做随笔作家吧？感觉会很好。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_00_19","textHome":"因为我这条命本该没有了才对……@所以总觉得有种不可思议的感觉……嗯。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":1}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_00_20","textHome":"这样的成长……@也是活着的喜悦之一……嗯。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":1}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_00_21","textHome":"正因为受了许多人的影响，@我才能活到现在……嗯。@所以，我应该用这被拯救的生命……@去真诚地面对别人。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":200}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_00_22","textHome":"这样的我……真的能改变吗……@我还没有什么自信……嗯。@但是……我想成为……不去在意悲伤，@而是细数着喜悦和幸福前行的人，@现在的我真的是这样想的……嗯。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_00_23","textHome":"我希望能拥有一样可以给我的心@带来光芒的东西，哪怕只有一个也好……@这样，即便有时哭泣……有时后悔……@也能继续活下去。因为，无论是@多么渺小的光亮……也不会被黑暗所抹消。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_51_24","textHome":"今天也请多关照……嗯。@还有，每天都很热呢……@啊，并不是不喜欢夏天……@我在说什么呢……对不起。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302500}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_51_25","textHome":"夏天的清晨，我很喜欢……嗯。@可以感受到耀眼的阳光。@但是，到了中午，就变成刺眼了……@有点难受……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":300}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_51_26","textHome":"说到日记，正常是在一天的结束时写的……@但偶尔也会在白天翻开日记本，@用和夜晚不同的心境来写……嗯。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":1}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_51_27","textHome":"夏日的夕阳……真美……@前阵子，买到了和这夕阳一样，@燃烧般橘红色的彩色铅笔，@用来在日记里画插图了……嗯。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":10.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":1}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_00_03","textHome":"对这个世界绝望了……@那个……这种事要怎么解释呢……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_51_28","textHome":"啊，烟花！我喜欢烟花，嗯。@无论是大号的烟花，还是闪亮的手持烟花棒，@只要静静地观看……就能让我安心……嗯。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":1}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_51_29","textHome":"刨冰，要吃吗？@你喜欢什么颜色的糖浆呢？@我的话，喜欢透明的……@梨花绝对会选草莓的吧……嗯。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":1}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_51_30","textHome":"那个……是不是……可以出发了呢？@没有！不是说为了方便出门才穿这件的……@嗯……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":1}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_51_31","textHome":"镜之魔女的结界，@不可思议地在夏天也很凉快……@为了不麻烦到别人，我太紧张了，@结果出了一身冷汗……嗯。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":1}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_51_32","textHome":"组队战斗以后，正打算在本子上写下记录……@为了不重复相同的失败……@才能平安迎接明年的夏天……嗯。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_51_33","textHome":"这件泳装……吗？@嗯，是从梨花帮我挑的那些里面……@选了看起来我也能穿的……@怎么样？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":11.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":100}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_51_34","textHome":"哇……海……好像从小时候到现在都……嗯。@波光粼粼……比想象中的还要美……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":100}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_51_35","textHome":"小学的时候，我很喜欢……暑假作业……嗯。@因为在作业里有图画日记，@可以把自己的日记写在后面……@完全不会厌烦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302500}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_51_36","textHome":"啊，请看。好漂亮的贝壳！@是珍珠贝……吗？@改变角度的话，光芒也会变化……@想带回去好好保管……嗯。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":100}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_51_37","textHome":"以前去学校上学是件非常难受的事，@放暑假就会感觉松了口气……嗯。@但现在，是因为能够自由地和朋友们见面，@所以喜欢暑假的……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":302500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":100}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_00_04","textHome":"我第一次……和这么多人说话……嗯。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":1}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":9.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_51_38","textHome":"我也想像随笔作家一样，@把各种体验写成文章……@所以，现在更应该做@只有夏天才能做的事……嗯。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":100}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_51_39","textHome":"哇，好厉害的积雨云！@虽然可能有些微不足道，但感觉很新鲜……@想死的时候，还觉得这世上@已经没有什么快乐的了……嗯。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":300}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_51_40","textHome":"彩色铅笔……想要很多，嗯。@因为想把和朋友们一起编织成的，@海边闪亮的回忆……@用记忆中的颜色记录下来……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"id":302500,"motion":1}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3025_51_41","textHome":"诶？诶？我的泳装……哪里不对吗？@难、难道穿反了……没有吧！嗯……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":302500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":302500,"motion":300}]}